name: DON'T PANIC THAT'S ACID
description:
Image produced as the cover of a 100% old school DJ set, which salutes the heydays of the Acid era. 

Listen for free on Soundcloud. 

This DJ set is a celebration of the golden age of Acid. From the birth of illegal raves, the discovery of XTC, to the sharpest sounds of TB-303. A celebration of sounds that were lost in time.
100% Old School set. Only tracks from 1990 - 2000

Don't panic
That's ACID!
